item.title: Prayer bpn10182 in Māori
item.description: *KIA TĀKINA IA RĀ, I TE ATA, I TE RĀNUI, I TE AHIAHI PŌ *Te tangata e hiahia ana ki te karakia, me horoi e ia ōna ringa, ā, i a ia e horoi ana ka mea ai a ia: Whakakahangia tōku ringa e tōku Atua, ka hopu pai ai ia i Tāu Pukapuka ki te pūkaha e kore e whaimana ngā manotini o te ao ki runga i a ia.
